verbose_text: After combination mechanical stretch with hBSMCs treatment, the protein levels of M2 and M3 were 2.845 +/-0.143 and 2.209 +/-0.113, respectively, and after combination no stretch with hBSMCs / ICCs treatment, M2, M3, and c-kit were 1.343 +/-0.094, 1.207 +/-0.077, and 1.433 +/-0.073, respectively.
